  First insert glue picture:
    if (EOS flag set) {    // old channel ends with EOS
        insert RAP with PCR
        reset EOS flag
    }
    insert glue picture

  Entry picture:
    if (EOS flag not set)
        insert EOS

    insert RAP with PCR


